title: Celebrity Gossip- Giving Up The Olympics For Acting
description: Kim Kardashian experienced her first “Take your kids to work day” and it didn’t go great… Plus, one famous actor was expected to go to the Olympics and get a college scholarship, but gave it up to star in a musical.
